               artifacts as specified in the attached test cases</li>
            <li>Interview: the IA will conduct discussions with individuals within the organization
               to facilitate assessor understanding, achieve clarification, or obtain evidence</li>
            <li>Technical Tests: the IA will perform technical tests, including penetration testing,
               on system components using automated and manual methods</li>
         </ul>
